column5:
Fix display of magit.<branch>.{merge,remote}

The variables were switched.

Closes #3778.

magit-push-popup: switch keys for --force{,-with-lease}

We only keep `--force' for users of older versions of Git.  The new and
better argument `--force-with-lease' should be what is easier to use.

replace magit-log-{verbose,nongraph}-{args => re}

Replace `magit-log-verbose-args' with `magit-log-verbose-re' and
replace `magit-log-nongraph-args' with `magit-log-nongraph-re'.

magit-diff-paths: bugfix

The fix is actually in `magit-diff-refresh-buffer';
do not append "--" if ARGS already contains that.

improve and document magit-section-{match,when,case}

Also adjust the output of `magit-describe-section' to be more useful
for people who have just read the doc-string of `magit-section-match.'

magit.texi: remove FAQ and ChangeLog

Remove the sparse FAQ and the outdated one-entry ChangeLog;
and instead link to the more up-to-date online information.

remove magit-{branch-no-remote,remote-part-of-branch}

Remove `magit-branch-no-remote' and `magit-remote-part-of-branch'.
Luckily they are no longer used anywhere.

magit-delete-branch: don't use magit-{remote-part-of-branch,branch-no-remote}

In `magit-delete-branch' don't use `magit-remote-part-of-branch' and
`magit-branch-no-remote'.  Instead do something much less complicated.

rename to magit-log-edit-prev-window-configuration

from `magit-pre-log-edit-window-configuration',
because it should have a `magit-log-edit-' prefix.

rename magit-{filename => magit-file-relative-name}

Rename `magit-filename' to `magit-file-relative-name' because it is
similar to built-in `file-relative-name'.  Also move its definition.

remove unused variables magit-wazzup-{head,all-p}

There *intended* purpose is already covered by `magit-mode-init' setting
`magit-refresh-args', like for other modes derived from `magit-mode'.

magit-bisect-skip doesn't take an argument; so don't pass one when calling it interactively

Fix for bug introduced in 5d1336a

@pjweisberg thanks
